lead_paragraph: The PGA Tour's West Coast swing certainly agrees with Brandt Snedeker who turns his attention to this week's Phoenix Open in Arizona just days after winning the weather-hit Farmers Insurance Open in San Diego.

headline.print_headline: West Coast Fan Snedeker Sets Sights on Phoenix
